                            About Us
                        

Albemarle is a leading specialty chemical company providing innovative chemistry solutions to customers in over 100 countries around the world.  We are committed to creating value for our shareholders, customers and employees, while continually striving for excellence by doing the right things the right way.
At Albemarle, we've built a thriving international business by envisioning a limitless future and putting innovation to work to improve people's lives. That's our culture. That's our commitment. And when you join our team, it's an opportunity you share with talented men and women around the globe. Anyone can give you a job. At Albemarle, we believe you deserve more. Something big enough to build a future. Big enough to change the world.
Are you ready to build a real future? Look to the company where big ideas and big opportunities happen every day. That's Albemarle, and we're always looking to hire the best talent-from recent graduates to seasoned business leaders-across all areas of our operations, including:

Accounting and Finance
Business/Product Management
Chemistry
Engineering (Chemical, Electrical, Mechanical, Civil, Industrial, Petroleum)
Health, Safety and Environmental Technology
 Human Resources
 Information Technology
 Manufacturing
 Purchasing
Sales and Marketing
 Software Development/Programming
